									<div data-country="Ethiopia" class="country">
										<div class="container-inner">
											<h3>Ethiopia</h3>

											<p>
												The choice of jurisdiction can make a big difference to
												any divorce outcome. Spousal maintenance for example, is
												restricted in Ethiopia. We advise clients in
												circumstances where they may have the choice to divorce
												in either Ethiopia or through the courts of England and
												Wales.
											</p>
