									</div>

									<div data-country="Finland" class="country">
										<div class="container-inner">
											<h3>Finland</h3>

											<p>
												Finland is a member state of the European Union and as
												such is party to the cross border regulations dealing
												with divorce. No grounds are required for a divorce in
												Finland.
											</p>
										</div>
									</div>

